alt_text: adidas - Your Future Is Not Mine
title: adidas - Your Future Is Not Mine (2016)
description: The 2016 Adidas commercial "Your Future is Not Mine," directed by Terence Neale, features influential creatives like Aleali May, Luka Sabbat, and Iman Shumpert, among others, who march confidently towards an optimistic future, challenging the preconceived notions of a dystopian tomorrow. This campaign, produced by the advertising agency Johannes Leonardo, emphasizes individual empowerment and the message that one's future is theirs to create, rallying viewers to defy negative expectations and shape their own destinies through creativity and personal initiative.
director: Exile Edit, Nate Gross, Shane Reid
tags: SHOWER | ADIDAS | HUNTER HAMPTON | MATTHEW EDWARDS | JEPH BURTON | WES PHELAN | JOHANNES LEONARDO | VR HEADSET

alt_text: Tiny Fallout New Vegas by Flurdeh
title: Tiny Fallout New Vegas by Flurdeh (2021)
description: Flurdeh specializes in applying a "tilt-shift" effect to video games, transforming their expansive 3D environments into charming miniature dioramas. The videos share common features such as accelerated animations and a lower framerate, enhancing their resemblance to stop-motion animation rather than modern video game footage.
director: Kevin Hensen

alt_text: Tiny Cyberpunk 2077 by Flurdeh
title: Tiny Cyberpunk 2077 by Flurdeh (2021)
description: Flurdeh specializes in applying a "tilt-shift" effect to video games, transforming their expansive 3D environments into charming miniature dioramas. The videos share common features such as accelerated animations and a lower framerate, enhancing their resemblance to stop-motion animation rather than modern video game footage. An example highlighted is Cyberpunk, where the game's diverse settings are miniaturized, and characters are depicted as if they were tiny figurines engaging in everyday activities.
director: Kevin Hensen
